      <title>巴西 12 月初年度通胀率超过所有经济学家预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/brazil-s-annual-inflation-tops-all-forecasts-in-early-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月初，巴西年度通胀放缓幅度低于预期，突显央行行长在降息同时试图在年底前将物价控制在容忍范围内所面临的困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/brazil-s-annual-inflation-tops-all-forecasts-in-early-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率乐观情绪推动欧洲股市在 2022 年 1 月附近保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/european-stocks-extend-year-end-rally-on-interest-rate-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市稳定，徘徊在 2022 年 1 月以来的最高水平附近，因人们对央行明年降息的乐观情绪日益增强，年底股市强劲上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/european-stocks-extend-year-end-rally-on-interest-rate-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:10:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
